1. *On joj je dao buket cveća.* (He gave her a bouquet of flowers.)
2. *Ona je s njom otišla na sledeći deo puta.* (She went with her on the next part of the journey.)
3. *On je njoj obećao da će je zaštititi.* (He promised her he would protect her.)
4. *Ona je njoj pokazala svoju novu haljinu.* (She showed her new dress to her.)
5. *On je njoj rekao da je voli.* (He told her he loves her.)